title: Garden Fresh Vegetarian Food
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Juice bar, Take-out, Taiwanese
description: A family-run veggie food cafe. Features a hot food bar where you choose your combo plate which comes with soup and barley grain rice. Also offers an an extensive la carte menu from snacks and soups to noodle and rice meals with faux meat. Has fresh juices and a range of frozen and prepared foods for take home (dumpling, steamed buns, etc.). No egg, onion, or MSG used. Small and informal. Lot parking available.
